OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fand the first part of the night will
OL,7,Fsee a few showers. Becoming dry in the
OL,8,Fearly hours with variable amounts of
OL,9,Fcloud.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FDry in the morning with some
OL,12,Fhazy sunshine. Clouding over in the
OL,13,Fafternoon with the showery rain
OL,14,Fspreading northeast, Shetland dry
OL,15,Funtil early evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
