OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOutbreaks
OL,6,Fof locally heavy rain spread northeast
OL,7,FFriday. This clears to sunny spells
OL,8,Fand the odd shower Saturday. Orkney
OL,9,Fwill become dry as the odd shower
OL,10,Fcontinues over Shetland Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
